               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">15th August [1871] ¶ Sir, ¶  ¶ I have the honor by direction of the above Committee ¶  to request that you will be good enough to deliver a lecture at this Institution on the 2nd of November next ¶ I ...</supplied>
